2. If you are fine with word accuracy let the user double click instead of click which will lead to selecting the word and see what is selected by [window.getSelection()](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/getSelection)

3. Grab the coordinates of the click and let&#39;s say the span has same font throughout with size of `z px` then the height and width of each letter will be more or less z pixels.

